snippet.title: Shopping with my Mom part1 #shorts
snippet.description:
https://gofund.me/3dd4f04b 

Sierra Rose & Rhia Quinn are two sweet and kind little sisters. They are Canadian Youtubers and love
entertaining people through their funny and educational videos on YouTube and TikTok, especially all the kids around the world. Their audience so far has reached 4 Million Subscribers Worldwide. Sierra & Rhia wants to go bigger than this... They want to make the world a better place.. Sierra's birthday wish is to turn into a "Santa Claus" and send lots of presents to kids in need, those who are sick in the hospital and those who are orphaned.
The girls donate their toys and clothes very often and buy new things for local kids in need.
They enjoy sharing, caring, and making people laugh.
Please support the little sisters in making the world a better and safe place for kids.
All the donations will go to the Alberta Children's Hospital and also to several local orphanages. We will keep you updated by uploading videos and photos through their journey and hope to spread kindness and help kids in need.
We thank every kind of person who supports the girls!
Together we can do this! (Parents of the Girls)




𝐒𝐔𝐁𝐒𝐂𝐑𝐈𝐁𝐄 Sierra and Rhia https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCe6n0z9UbsxYCS8P83f84tw
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/princess_sierra_rose/
